title: Lizard Habitat
description: An illustration depicting a lizard in its natural habitat. The scene shows a rock covered in moss, with a lizard resting nearby. There are three suns in the background, suggesting a bright, sunny environment. The ground is covered with small pebbles and sand, creating a realistic setting for the lizard.

title: Brown Snake on Ground
description: A brown snake is coiled on the ground, surrounded by fallen leaves and small green plants. The snake has a smooth, shiny appearance and blends in with the earthy tones of the environment.
